description	"Lobot

Class: Hero.
Class Summary: 
A speedy grenadier with a Wrench melee weapon. 

Weaponry:
- Relby-K23 (Based on Westar pistol level 2)
- Wrench
- Frag Nades (3)
- Concussion Nades (2)

* Special Weaponry Descriptions:
--- Wrench
- No defense
- Cannot block sabers or blasters
- Can block force push/pull by blocking
- Has high knockback and can send enemies airborne

Inventory:
- Sentry Gun

Attributes:
- Blast Armor
- Heal (2)
- Shield Recharge (1)
- Radar Scanner (Perma-sense 1)

Abilities:
- Dodge (3) [Class Special 1]
- Dash (2) [Alt Ability 1]

Lobot was a male human from the planet Bespin who, with the assistance of his AJ6 cyborg construct, was paid to run battlefield calculations for the Galactic Empire. However, he eventually began working with the smuggler Lando Calrissian aboard the Millennium Falcon, running numerous criminal jobs."